cern.extjfx.test

Annotation Type RunInFxThread


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
public @interface RunInFxThread
    Indicates that given method should be executed within FX Application Thread. Will work only the test class runs with FxJUnit4Runner.
